sources.title: Room 203 | Full Movie | Horror Thriller | Francesca Xuereb | Viktoria Vinyarska
sources.description:
When lifelong friends Kim and Izzy move to the city to get away from Kim's controlling parents and Izzy's personal demons stemming from a suicide attempt, they into ROOM 203, a quirky apartment with a large stained-glass window that depicts medieval sacrifices. But the friends soon become concerned when ROOM 203 reveals unmistakable signs of a haunting that culminates in visions of a menacing crow, and Izzy's rapid mental and emotional decline. With help from her college boyfriend Ian, Kim discovers that many residents of ROOM 203 have disappeared since the murder-suicide of a married couple exactly fifty years ago. Izzy soon becomes possessed by the demonic spirit, MORRIGU, which commands Izzy to sacrifice herself. To save Izzy's life, Kim may need to sacrifice her own.
2022.  Stars: Francesca Xuereb, Viktoria Vinyarska, Eric Wiegand
